title: Luka Keeps the Lakers Spiraling
description:
Jalen & Jacoby have a lot to say about Luka's performance against Lakers. Dunked on Dwight. Iso buckets against LeBron. Russ going back at Luka and... struggling. LeBron isn't the only star in the Play-in bracket currently - out East the Nets are scuffling, waiting for the stars to arrive, is there enough time to get it together? Also, the Packers GM says NOBODY is calling him about Rodgers, and the Giants are willing to take calls on Saquon?? Tap in with the team!
